00:34:08.310 --> 00:34:10.979
So let's put that out over here.

00:34:20.550 --> 00:34:23.630
So that's another definition.

00:34:23.630 --> 00:34:28.929
We say that a and
b are relatively

00:34:28.929 --> 00:34:39.610
