01:08:55.569 --> 01:08:56.399
OK.

01:08:56.399 --> 01:08:58.400
So let's continue.

01:09:07.620 --> 01:09:09.080
We consider two cases.

01:09:09.080 --> 01:09:14.439
If the remainder of b and
a is unequal to 0, well,

01:09:14.439 --> 01:09:17.600
